rComments: One of the best professors I have ever had at UofT! I never cared about American history before taking his class; he's inspired me to take more and perhaps even pursue it for grad school. Lectures were always so interesting, he really knew how to engage the class. Also very approachable, so asking for help was never an issue. 10/10 would recommend!
